== Plum Notes

Written By: Kevin Incorvia
Purpose: A simple note taking application with support for tagging
Version: .1

== About

Plum notes is an open source Notes application.  The authentication system was built following the guidelines of "Ruby on Rails 3 Tutorial" by Michael Hartl.  Some of the features of Plum Notes includes:

* HTML formatting within notes
* Tag notes via "@" symbol (i.e. @tag)
* Uses Twitter Bootstrap framework